  "detailed_description": "At its core, Fragsurf is a competitive PvP game with complete multiplayer support, built and tested thoroughly over the years, revolving around the central mechanics of surfing and bunnyhopping.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEngage in high-speed combat, or explore other gamemodes such as tricksurf, kz, and speedrunning if you're looking for a more passive experience.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor creators, Fragsurf has full support for Steam Workshop and a lightweight yet powerful level creation tool.",
